 "components": {
  "task_instruction": "You are a precise text classifier. Read the input text and assign it to exactly one of the categories defined below.",
  "label::alarm_query": "",
  "label::alarm_set": "Assign to alarm_set if the text requests to set an alarm or timed alert that is not associated with a specific event, but rather serves as a general notification or countdown (e.g., \"set an alarm for 7 AM\", \"repeat alarm\", or \"remind me in 10 minutes\"). Choose alarm_set vs calendar_set if the request is only for a time-based alert without an explicit event or appointment.",
  "label::calendar_query": "",
  "label::calendar_remove": "",
  "label::calendar_set": "Assign to calendar_set if the text asks to schedule, add, or set a reminder for an event at a specific date or time, such as meetings, appointments, or personal reminders (e.g., \"remind me about the office meeting tomorrow at seven\"). Decide calendar_set vs alarm_set by whether the reminder is tied to a personal event or appointment (calendar_set) vs a simple timed alert or countdown (alarm_set).",
  "label::cooking_recipe": "",
  "label::datetime_query": "",
  "label::email_query": "",
  "label::email_sendemail": "",
  "label::general_quirky": "Assign to general_quirky if the text is an open-ended or conversational request for miscellaneous facts, comments, or information that does not ask for a concrete fact, direct definition, or specific recommendation—especially for topics about people, places, or things (e.g., \"tell me about rihana\", \"has the celebrity done any charitable work?\", or \"say something interesting about cheetahs\"). Decide general_quirky vs qa_factoid or recommendation_locations by whether the request is for a general discussion, overview, or an open prompt rather than a specific, concrete answer or suggestion.",
  "label::iot_hue_lightoff": "",
  "label::lists_createoradd": "",
  "label::lists_query": "",
  "label::lists_remove": "",
  "label::music_query": "",
  "label::news_query": "",
  "label::play_audiobook": "",
  "label::play_music": "",
  "label::play_podcasts": "",
  "label::play_radio": "",
  "label::qa_currency": "",
  "label::qa_definition": "",
  "label::qa_factoid": "Assign to qa_factoid if the text directly asks for a specific and concrete factual answer, such as a number, date, birthplace, or other narrow detail (e.g., \"how tall is rihanna?\", \"where was Einstein born?\"). Decide qa_factoid vs general_quirky by whether the input asks for a direct fact (qa_factoid) versus an open-ended, general overview or descriptive information (general_quirky).",
  "label::qa_stock": "",
  "label::recommendation_events": "",
  "label::recommendation_locations": "",
  "label::social_post": "",
  "label::takeaway_order": "",
  "label::transport_query": "",
